 32042                           ;	Multi-vector enable bit
 32043                           ;	MVECEN = ON, Multi-vector enabled, Vector table used for interrupts
 32044                           ;	IVTLOCK bit One-way set enable bit
 32045                           ;	IVT1WAY = ON, IVTLOCKED bit can be cleared and set only once
 32046                           ;	Low Power BOR Enable bit
